-- HSBC Hires Wingfield for Leveraged and Acquisition Finance
-- B y   W e n d y   M o c k
-- 2012-01-16T04:59:35Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-16/hsbc-hires-wingfield-for-leveraged-and-acquisition-finance-1-.html
HSBC Holdings Plc (HSBA)  hired Simon
Wingfield as a director on its Asia-Pacific leveraged and
acquisition finance team.  Hong Kong-based Wingfield reports to Lyndon Hsu, head of
leveraged and acquisition finance, Asia-Pacific, also based in
 Hong Kong . Wingfield was previously with National Australia Bank
Ltd., based in Melbourne.  Wingfield, who started with the London-based bank this
month, confirmed his new role when contacted by telephone today.
Elisha Vincent, Sydney-based spokeswoman for NAB, declined to
